Package fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.structure

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    A StructuralFeature of a simple key/value pair.
    Classifier
    A MetaClassifier which can be typed.
    Identifier
    The identifier of a Classifier.
    MetaClassifier
    A simple element identified by a Namespace and its name inside it.
    NamedElement
    An element which has a name.
    Namespace
    A namespace identified by a prefix and a URI.
    Namespace.Registry
    Registry of all declared Namespace.
    Reference
    A StructuralFeature of a link between two Classifier.
    StructuralFeature
    A simple structural feature which can be either a reference or an attribute.
